						               													<description>In this running/dice game the Smurfs organize a race, each player chooses a figure, the Smurf cards are placed face down on the game board at the beginning. The player on the turn rolls the dice once and moves on by the number of dice rolled, whoever rolls a 6 may roll the dice again and move, foreign figures are skipped, there can be several figures on one field. At the end of the turn, you perform the event that belongs to the square you landed on - on some squares you get cards that bring you to Gargamel's castle or save you from it. The first player to get his figure back to the start/finish square is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
